---
description: Project boundary rules for GroundSealWorkflowRuntime
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repository exists to build GroundSealWorkflowRuntime, not a general-purpose agent platform.
- Keep work aligned to the subsystem focus: state models, node contracts, checkpoints, approval interruption, resume semantics, deterministic branching, and workflow diagnostics.
- Before implementation, map each task to a roadmap phase.
- Do not add neighboring subsystems unless the integration contract explicitly requires it.
- Favor clarity, contracts, and evaluability over scope growth.
